WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.109
Hey, good morning, family.

00:00:01.109 --> 00:00:02.390
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:02.390 --> 00:00:05.195
Well, I have some things on my heart to talk to you about.

00:00:05.195 --> 00:00:09.013
I saw some things in the spirit, and I'm going to talk to you about it.

00:00:09.763 --> 00:00:16.744
First off, I just want to say thank you for all your support, the likes, the subscriptions, all of it.

00:00:16.744 --> 00:00:25.320
It is a blessing to our family, and we just want to say thank you, because you are helping get the gospel spread throughout the whole world.

00:00:25.320 --> 00:00:29.226
Literally, people's lives are being changed, and I just want to say thank you.

00:00:29.226 --> 00:00:38.063
All I know is that God put me on here and He told me to come and tell you all the things that are heavy in the spirit that we can pray about.

00:00:38.063 --> 00:00:45.355
Some things we can stop, some things we can't, but I know beyond a shadow of a doubt Jesus is coming, and He's coming soon.

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:49.550
So I want you to be looking up, for your redemption draws nigh.

00:00:54.012 --> 00:01:01.288
Late last night, I was praying and I saw a video that Perry Stone put out.

00:01:08.510 --> 00:01:13.964
There are a lot of times I'm praying and seeing stuff and I'm like, 'Lord, is there anybody else seeing anything?

00:01:13.964 --> 00:01:20.848
Is there anybody else having warnings about what's coming other than me?

00:01:20.848 --> 00:01:38.650
' I don't want to be a lone ranger out there, and I want to know that there are other prophetic confirmations about what's coming and about warnings.

00:01:38.650 --> 00:01:47.680
I clicked on the video to see what Perry Stone said the Lord showed him.

00:01:52.000 --> 00:02:29.453
In that video, which I'm going to show you a little clip of right here—to protect this man, I will never tell you what state he's in, what city he's in, or who he is—he said the same person who reported that, and it was accurate two weeks later, has said the next attack is going to be the power grid in the United States.

00:02:35.857 --> 00:02:40.869
The US grid, and I've seen many articles on this, is extremely vulnerable to cyberattacks.

00:02:40.869 --> 00:02:57.115
This person has stated from his information there will be an attack coming somewhere between August and the election.

00:02:57.115 --> 00:03:11.435
People are talking about an October surprise; maybe this is the October surprise, I don't know, but it will happen at some point.

00:03:17.115 --> 00:03:18.768
If it doesn't happen this year, this is absolutely going to happen.

00:03:18.768 --> 00:03:23.599
So you all see what he's saying?

00:03:34.599 --> 00:03:34.977
He has a warning from the Holy Ghost, it sounds like, from this man.

00:03:34.977 --> 00:03:52.799
I don't know who that man was, he doesn't even say, but it's a warning about them attacking the power grid from August to the elections in certain cities.

00:03:56.815 --> 00:03:57.810
I saw Philadelphia, I saw Chicago, I saw New York.

00:04:07.795 --> 00:04:08.150
I saw major cities going without power for three weeks.

00:04:09.217 --> 00:04:12.990
The Lord warned me to prepare and to tell you all.

00:04:23.649 --> 00:04:23.898
He's saying that this guy from the dark web is saying it would be three weeks, just like the Lord showed me.

00:04:23.898 --> 00:04:32.449
Sit and ask yourself: how would my family, my grandbabies, and I survive if we had to go two to three weeks without electricity?

00:04:32.449 --> 00:04:40.370
Because it's very possible in some places that an outage could last that long.

00:04:40.370 --> 00:04:44.240
I got that in prayer.

00:04:56.876 --> 00:04:57.098
I don't have secret intel, I don't work for the CIA.

00:04:57.098 --> 00:05:18.855
People ask me if I work for the CIA; I work for the Holy Spirit, and He will show you things to come and He will warn you so that you're not caught off guard.

00:05:18.855 --> 00:05:29.240
He always comes to His people and warns them if you're close to Him.

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:37.039
It's not just about me, it's about the body of Christ.

00:05:37.039 --> 00:05:42.669
It's about you building a relationship with the Lord.

00:05:49.271 --> 00:05:49.515
He wants to talk to you and tell you things to come.

00:06:00.960 --> 00:06:01.520
I'm nothing special; I want you to understand that He comes and talks to me because I've developed a relationship with Him.

00:06:05.259 --> 00:06:08.519
So, He will tell me things and He warns me of a lot.

00:06:10.840 --> 00:06:17.817
I usually say if the Lord hasn't said anything, I take it that it's not going to happen.

00:06:17.817 --> 00:06:20.440
Does that make sense?

00:06:20.440 --> 00:06:22.991
Because we are that close.

00:06:31.740 --> 00:06:41.800
I just believe with all my heart He's going to warn me, and if He doesn't say it, I don't believe it's coming in that area.

00:06:41.800 --> 00:06:55.621
If He warns me it's coming, that means He wants me to pray about it so we can stop it.

00:06:55.621 --> 00:07:17.599
When Perry Stone came out and said this and warned about the three weeks of power outage, it went alongside what the Holy Spirit warned me to tell you all.

00:07:17.599 --> 00:07:20.749
Let every word be established.

00:07:20.749 --> 00:07:25.182
There's something going on with the power grid.

00:07:25.182 --> 00:07:50.879
I told you all I believe if you are a person who has to have electricity for medical equipment or whatever, that you should try, if you can, to get some kind of solar power from Amazon.

00:07:53.759 --> 00:07:56.829
