00:07:56.829 --> 00:08:08.855
Then the Lord showed me three-phase power generators—like gasoline, propane, and natural gas generators—that would sustain long-term power.

00:08:08.855 --> 00:08:22.346
It would not run out of fuel because gas stations and banks would be closed during these power outages.

00:08:32.120 --> 00:08:32.331
It was a serious situation that they were going to try to do.

00:08:32.331 --> 00:08:36.099
He was even talking about an October surprise.

00:08:36.099 --> 00:08:38.248
Now, is it the October surprise?

00:08:39.715 --> 00:08:46.984
I told you all I believe there's a major event going to take place in October.

00:08:53.827 --> 00:08:55.500
I'm still praying over it.

00:08:55.500 --> 00:08:58.800
If it comes and goes and nothing happens, it's because we're praying over it.

00:08:58.800 --> 00:09:02.885
That's what the Lord's called me to do.

00:09:04.897 --> 00:09:14.040
