00:10:01.431 --> 00:10:05.500
Remember I told you I've seen it twice?

00:10:05.500 --> 00:10:11.920
There were all these fifty-gallon drums stacked up with 'Dollar Crash' written on the side.

00:10:11.920 --> 00:10:20.931
Well, this time the Lord showed me the dam had cracks all in the front of it.

00:10:20.931 --> 00:10:45.994
Some of them were big stress cracks, some of them were pin-fine cracks, but there was a center place in the middle of the dam and, all of a sudden, it was like spider-webbing out, splitting all around the center and splintering out.

00:10:45.994 --> 00:10:49.653
