00:10:51.320 --> 00:11:02.340
It was nasty; you could see putrid, gross, stinky stuff coming out of those cracks in this United States Economy Dam.

00:11:07.610 --> 00:11:13.800
The Lord showed me that dam is starting to get stress cracks and starting to break.

00:11:16.280 --> 00:11:25.472
